                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1795-18430612 t18430612-1795-punishment-71"></join>Confined for One Year</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Fourth Jury, before Edward Buttock, Esq.</hi>
